    "body" : "<p>Please stick to the nio API to perform these checks</p>\n\n<pre><code>import java.nio.file.*;\n\nstatic Boolean isDir(Path path) {\n  if (path == null || !Files.exists(path)) return false;\n  else return Files.isDirectory(path);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
